Class SampleVTI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.derby.vti.VTITemplate
      • org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.util.SampleVTI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.sql.ResultSet, java.sql.Wrapper, org.apache.derby.vti.AwareVTI

    public class SampleVTI
extends org.apache.derby.vti.VTITemplate
    A very simple, read-only, sample VTI.

    This VTI is incomplete and has its quirks - it is intended for basic testing only! Supported getters:

    • getString
    • getInt
